Originally Ron Rhumplekos home system of Oomp the systems star is now contained within a Dyson sphere leaving all the planets of the system to become frozen wastelands. The inside of the sphere however is a veritable wonderland of exotic plants, animals and machinery.
Not a great deal is known about the inner working of the sphere due to the companies secretive operations though every 10 sol standard years exactly they have open days with very limited admittance, there have been reports of people not leaving these events though the company insists they stayed of their own free will to work for the company.

